=== Implementation Notes ===

- Modified migrate.go to support multi-statement SQL files (split on ; delimiter).
  Required because EXCHANGE TABLES/RENAME cannot be expressed in a single statement.
- Used toDateTime (not toDateTime64) for TTL/PARTITION to match ClickHouse's
  requirement that TTL expressions resolve to DateTime type.
- ClickHouse internally normalizes INTERVAL 90 DAY to toIntervalDay(90) in system.tables.

Files changed:
- backend/internal/mdgateway/chmigrate/006_md_ticks_v2.sql (new)
- backend/internal/mdgateway/chmigrate/007_md_bars_v2.sql (new)
- backend/internal/mdgateway/chmigrate/migrate.go (multi-statement support)

